2. `/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/elementor/includes/managers/image.php` - get_lightbox_image_attributes implementation
3. `/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/elementor/includes/base/widget-base.php` - add_lightbox_data_attributes implementation
4. `/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/wordpress/wp-content/mu-plugins/gallery-attachment-title.php` - Existing the_title filter fix
5. `/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/wordpress/wp-content/mu-plugins/bit-crossblog-attachment-fix.php` - Cache warming for cross-blog attachments

