- `/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/wordpress/wp-content/mu-plugins/gallery-attachment-title.php` -- Remove or scope this file; its `the_title` filter is ineffective for the lightbox bug and risky for 244 colliding IDs
- `/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/elementor-pro/modules/gallery/widgets/gallery.php` -- Reference only: confirms the two gallery data structures (`$settings['gallery']` vs `$settings['galleries']`) at lines 78-131 and the render flow at lines 1449-1668
